                    <span class="font-medium"
                      >Is it better to cut sugar completely?</span
                    >
                    <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">+</span>
                  </button>
                  <div
                    class="px-4 pb-3 hidden faq-answer text-sm text-gray-700"
                  >
                    For most people, a
                    <strong>realistic and sustainable goal</strong> is to reduce
                    added sugar to within recommended limits, not necessarily to
                    zero. Completely eliminating sugar can be difficult and may
                    lead to rebound cravings. Gradual, consistent reductions are
                    usually more successful long term.
                  </div>
