                    Artificial and non-nutritive sweeteners (such as aspartame,
                    sucralose, stevia) do not contribute sugar grams or calories
                    in the same way, so they are
                    <strong>not counted as added sugar</strong> in this
                    calculator. However, research on their long-term effects is
                    still evolving. If you use them, it’s wise to do so in
                    moderation and focus primarily on whole, minimally processed
                    foods.
                  </div>
